{
    "text": "\ud83d\udccdVienna, Austria \ud83c\udde6\ud83c\uddf9  Have you ever visited Vienna?\u2728\u2708\ud83d\udcf8\ud83c\udf0f\u2764 Tag a friend you would like to go to Austria with  Follow \u2014> @escapetoeurope  Follow \u2014> @escapetoasia_  \ud83e\udde0Vienna ranks first in the cultivation of cucumbers. Yes, you understood correctly Austria is the agrarian leader of such a vegetable crop as a cucumber. Tomatoes and different types of greens are also among the top five. Therefore, when you come to Vienna, be sure to try a salad of these vegetables with Kern\u00f6l pumpkin oil in a cafe\u2757  Credit to @vienna_images   #escapetoeurope #europe #travel #travels #travelblogger #earth #placestovisit #dreamdestinations #discovertheglobe #travelaway #travelenthusiast #travelforlife #traveldestinations #travelblog #travelblogger #travellingthroughtheworld #beautifuldestinations #traveloften #picoftheday #travelineurope #travelaway #topdestinations #travelstagram #travelphotography #instaeurope  #viennaaustria #viennagram #austriagram #visitaustria #austria\ud83c\udde6\ud83c\uddf9",
